70" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Stevie-Wonder-and-Kamala-Harris.-CREDIT_-Daniel-Knighton_Getty-Images-and-REBECCA-NOBLE_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Stevie-Wonder-and-Kamala-Harris.-CREDIT_-Daniel-Knighton_Getty-Images-and-REBECCA-NOBLE_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Stevie-Wonder-and-Kamala-Harris.-CREDIT_-Daniel-Knighton_Getty-Images-and-REBECCA-NOBLE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Stevie-Wonder-and-Kamala-Harris.-CREDIT_-Daniel-Knighton_Getty-Images-and-REBECCA-NOBLE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Stevie-Wonder-and-Kamala-Harris.-CREDIT_-Daniel-Knighton_Getty-Images-and-REBECCA-NOBLE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Stevie-Wonder-and-Kamala-Harris.-CREDIT_-Daniel-Knighton_Getty-Images-and-REBECCA-NOBLE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Stevie-Wonder-and-Kamala-Harris.-CREDIT_-Daniel-Knighton_Getty-Images-and-REBECCA-NOBLE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-wonder">史蒂夫·旺德 (Stevie Wonder)</a>在与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spike-lee">斯派克·李 (Spike Lee)</a>合作的新政治广告中认可<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris)</a>为美国下一任总统。</p><p>哈里斯在 Twitter/X 上分享了这段视频，并看到旺德在与李的对话中讨论了他与她的友谊。</p><p> “早在人们知道卡马拉是谁之前，我就对她感到兴奋，”旺德说。 “我对未来感到非常高兴。我很高兴，因为我知道并相信她将成为美国的下一任总统。”</p><p> “不是为了让你们感到难过，但这需要一个女人，”他继续说道。 “但不仅仅是任何一个女人，一个很棒的女人。而且她始终如一地完成了这项工作。”查看下面的完整剪辑。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">史蒂夫·旺德是我的老朋友。</p><p>我感谢他成为我们为未来而奋斗的一部分。</p><p>加入我们： <a href="https://t.co/MKvOQGgN2t">https://t.co/MKvOQ